snippet: The Haitian prime minister who resigned under pressure over the weekend said Monday that the country has made significant progress during his tenure even as the political standoff that led to his ouster continues....

headline.print_headline: Haiti PM Defends Tenure After Forced Resignation
headline.main: Haiti PM Defends Tenure After Forced Resignation

lead_paragraph: The Haitian prime minister who resigned under pressure over the weekend said Monday that the country has made significant progress during his tenure even as the political standoff that led to his ouster continues.
